{"tid":1752382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好太驕傲住。 我哋贏係因為單議席單票制嘅缺憾。","createTime":"2019-11-24T20:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T21:09:38.000Z","uid":147803,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"337939e3195135f46014a4989bf82b0cb71774d1","tid":1752382,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:03:49.000Z","msg":"兩邊支持者嘅比例都仲係64比左右<br />\n<br />\n今次我哋贏到開巷純粹係單議席單票制度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會選舉係用比例代表制。 係呢個制度之後我哋唔會再有今日嘅成果。<br />\n<br />\n另外個人預言 選區將會使用傑利蠑螈嘅方法重新劃分， 下次區議會選舉將會更加難打<br />\n<br />\n我哋要做嘅係令到更加中立嘅人支持我哋！ 鞏固勢力<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好驕傲但都唔好氣餒<br />\n<br />\nkeep 住上！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9dcd1004bd6e8cdcc3827f64d7c71164c0fe84","tid":1752382,"uid":59965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:05:00.000Z","msg":"正確 唔好開心得咁早住<br />\n<br />\n未點完先講 提下大家今次區選有咩意義同代價<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1752306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1752306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a47014c0abb1fd68dba112c4afa3631d6e00461","tid":1752382,"uid":125453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92593df296a094ffc93b80b3902d16774e9a8a8","tid":1752382,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:14:49.000Z","msg":"自推 3"},{"pid":"0c1a1981b478a7ffd3c06b57d9a4188e05a57d65","tid":1752382,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:16:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d4552171a0e881d3233de449ac6e25fca1270c0","tid":1752382,"uid":233054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:17:39.000Z","msg":"正視聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e6516cd42f1a4a6fd95ae435fd934d87d6f3dc","tid":1752382,"uid":22701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:17:43.000Z","msg":"比例代表制先係缺陷囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb71f437d31a3289b4f5d27b2b93bcd3f5066998","tid":1752382,"uid":85444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:18:52.000Z","msg":"啱 只要利用今次既結果 因為我地要投既都投哂<br />\n政府建制就可以係立法會配好票 <br />\n到時就係佢地大勝"},{"pid":"c8a1a2c5812017c59cf8421ce150c5686dd7d8f5","tid":1752382,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:19:21.000Z","msg":"有功能組别講條春咩"},{"pid":"eac3b60314a88138ee14b72efe4a9e36f2f30b70","tid":1752382,"uid":91422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:20:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e37c28782c847db3369b64238e24d1b52174978","tid":1752382,"uid":254123,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:20:15.000Z","msg":"不如你諗下對面種左幾多票啦<br />\n<br />\n本來就冇可能會全部人都支持你<br />\n<br />\n但種果啲票我估都帶10-20%<br />\n<br />\n即係話 我地大約有7成人支持<br />\n<br />\n好足夠了"},{"pid":"3046360df9afa03257b12982f8848de1f8eff310","tid":1752382,"uid":196329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"47e6516cd42f1a4a6fd95ae435fd934d87d6f3dc","tid":1752382,"uid":22701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:17:43.000Z","msg":"比例代表制先係缺陷囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:21:12.000Z","msg":"其實冇話缺憾<br />\n區議員因為本身只係處理地區問題<br />\n所以就由當區居民投票，高票者勝，係好合理<br />\n至於立法會就因要處理全港政策既審議<br />\n所以會用比例代表制務求有一定支持既少數都有辦法進入議會<br />\n呢個設置係好合理<br />\n唔合理既只係DQ，功能組別等等既香港特色姐"},{"pid":"d3aefaf65bd55ca678d7a6ee44260a9c9c06c798","tid":1752382,"uid":294148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e37c28782c847db3369b64238e24d1b52174978","tid":1752382,"uid":254123,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:20:15.000Z","msg":"不如你諗下對面種左幾多票啦<br />\n<br />\n本來就冇可能會全部人都支持你<br />\n<br />\n但種果啲票我估都帶10-20%<br />\n<br />\n即係話 我地大約有7成人支持<br />\n<br />\n好足夠了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:21:57.000Z","msg":"但下次佢地都係一車車咁種票<br />\n都係有10-20%<br />\n所以我都支持要拉攏更多敵人做自己友"},{"pid":"ca1dcc65e0d97d3929b766743afb3771d7d13c2d","tid":1752382,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3046360df9afa03257b12982f8848de1f8eff310","tid":1752382,"uid":196329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"47e6516cd42f1a4a6fd95ae435fd934d87d6f3dc","tid":1752382,"uid":22701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:17:43.000Z","msg":"比例代表制先係缺陷囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:21:12.000Z","msg":"其實冇話缺憾<br />\n區議員因為本身只係處理地區問題<br />\n所以就由當區居民投票，高票者勝，係好合理<br />\n至於立法會就因要處理全港政策既審議<br />\n所以會用比例代表制務求有一定支持既少數都有辦法進入議會<br />\n呢個設置係好合理<br />\n唔合理既只係DQ，功能組別等等既香港特色姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:23:45.000Z","msg":"贊成<br />\n<br />\n區議會單議席單票冇乜問題。 係今次畀大家當咗公投先至有問題<br />\n<br />\n不過 政府真係捉蟲入屎忽<br />\n就算真係搞公投可能比例都係64，73<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家以議席例係81甚至91<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bee1aaf80fb061012a8f04d164194f434edbf4f","tid":1752382,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:27:59.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"8403532f1edbc3d9ae5c1feca97dc3313c8bf20c","tid":1752382,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:31:47.000Z","msg":"大家宜家要做既就係將種票掌心雷推上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打蛇隨棍上唔好比佢停<br />\nKO 埋建制個10-20%鐵票"},{"pid":"b049783df7ce1d7248223681389da0aeea27cec7","t